---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Docs at FOSDEM — Docs" description="Watch the talks about Docs presented at FOSDEM 2025 and FOSDEM 2026, covering the project's history, its European collaboration model, and how it's built on foundational open-source libraries.">
  <Header current="fosdem" />

<main id="top">

  <!-- ================= INTRO ================= -->
  <section class="article">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="eyebrow reveal in">Community</div>
      <h1 class="reveal in">Docs at FOSDEM</h1>
      <p>Every year, FOSDEM in Brussels brings together the free and open-source software community for two days of talks. In 2025 and 2026, Virgile Deville — Product Manager of Docs — went there to present the project: how it's built, who funds it, and how it collaborates with the libraries it depends on.</p>
      <p>Below are recordings of every talk, straight from the FOSDEM video archive.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================= FOSDEM 2026 ================= -->
  <section id="fosdem-2026">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <div class="eyebrow">FOSDEM 2026</div>
        <h2>Three talks in Brussels</h2>
        <p>Docs was covered from three angles: the product itself, the libraries it's built on, and where it fits in the Local First movement.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="talk-list">

        <div class="talk-card reveal">
          <div class="talk-video">
            <video controls preload="none">
              <source src="https://video.fosdem.org/2026/ud2208/VDZR7S-lasuite-docs.mp4" type="video/mp4">
              <source src="https://video.fosdem.org/2026/ud2208/VDZR7S-lasuite-docs.av1.webm" type="video/webm">
            </video>
          </div>
          <div class="talk-body">
            <div class="talk-meta">
              <span class="status-pill shipped">FOSDEM 2026</span>
              <span class="funder-pill">Tool the Docs</span>
            </div>
            <h3><a href="https://fosdem.org/2026/schedule/event/VDZR7S-lasuite-docs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LaSuite Docs: open source collaborative documentation platform</a></h3>
            <p class="talk-desc">A tour of Docs as a block-based, open-source editor built by the French and German governments: real-time collaboration, granular permissions, sub-documents, and a headless CMS API — and why it suits teams looking to build, manage, and scale documentation.</p>
            <div class="talk-links">
              <a href="https://fosdem.org/2026/schedule/event/VDZR7S-lasuite-docs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Event page</a>
              <span class="sep-dot">·</span>
              <a href="https://video.fosdem.org/2026/ud2208/VDZR7S-lasuite-docs.mp4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Download video</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="talk-card reveal">
          <div class="talk-video">
            <video controls preload="none">
              <source src="https://video.fosdem.org/2026/aw1120/DC97FQ-building_digital_workplace_solutions_on_top_of_foundational_libraries_blocknote_.mp4" type="video/mp4">
              <source src="https://video.fosdem.org/2026/aw1120/DC97FQ-building_digital_workplace_solutions_on_top_of_foundational_libraries_blocknote_.av1.webm" type="video/webm">
            </video>
          </div>
          <div class="talk-body">
            <div class="talk-meta">
              <span class="status-pill shipped">FOSDEM 2026</span>
              <span class="funder-pill">Building Europe's Public Digital Infrastructure</span>
            </div>
            <h3><a href="https://fosdem.org/2026/schedule/event/DC97FQ-building_digital_workplace_solutions_on_top_of_foundational_libraries_blocknote_/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Building digital workplace solutions on top of foundational libraries</a></h3>
            <p class="talk-desc">With Yousef El-Dardiry. How France and Germany fund core features — exports, comments, edit attribution, suggestions — directly into BlockNote and Yjs rather than into Docs alone, why funding libraries differs from funding applications, and what the whole ecosystem gains from it.</p>
            <div class="talk-links">
              <a href="https://fosdem.org/2026/schedule/event/DC97FQ-building_digital_workplace_solutions_on_top_of_foundational_libraries_blocknote_/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Event page</a>
              <span class="sep-dot">·</span>
              <a href="https://video.fosdem.org/2026/aw1120/DC97FQ-building_digital_workplace_solutions_on_top_of_foundational_libraries_blocknote_.mp4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Download video</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="talk-card reveal">
          <div class="talk-video">
            <video controls preload="none">
              <source src="https://video.fosdem.org/2026/k3201/U3PPYW-local-first-collaborative-workspace.mp4" type="video/mp4">
              <source src="https://video.fosdem.org/2026/k3201/U3PPYW-local-first-collaborative-workspace.av1.webm" type="video/webm">
            </video>
          </div>
          <div class="talk-body">
            <div class="talk-meta">
              <span class="status-pill shipped">FOSDEM 2026</span>
              <span class="funder-pill">Local-First, sync engines, CRDTs</span>
            </div>
            <h3><a href="https://fosdem.org/2026/schedule/event/U3PPYW-local-first-collaborative-workspace/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">A Local First collaborative workplace?</a></h3>
            <p class="talk-desc">A lightning talk introducing LaSuite, DINUM's MIT-licensed suite built around Docs, Drive, Meet, and an AI assistant, and its reusable UI Kit — offered as a resource for the Local First community building its own collaborative apps.</p>
            <div class="talk-links">
              <a href="https://fosdem.org/2026/schedule/event/U3PPYW-local-first-collaborative-workspace/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Event page</a>
              <span class="sep-dot">·</span>
              <a href="https://video.fosdem.org/2026/k3201/U3PPYW-local-first-collaborative-workspace.mp4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Download video</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================= FOSDEM 2025 ================= -->
  <section id="fosdem-2025" style="background:var(--gray-025);">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <div class="eyebrow">FOSDEM 2025</div>
        <h2>Where the European collaboration started</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="talk-list">

        <div class="talk-card reveal">
          <div class="talk-video">
            <video controls preload="none">
              <source src="https://video.fosdem.org/2025/aw1126/fosdem-2025-6403-note-worthy-collaboration-co-developing-a-note-taking-application.mp4" type="video/mp4">
              <source src="https://video.fosdem.org/2025/aw1126/fosdem-2025-6403-note-worthy-collaboration-co-developing-a-note-taking-application.av1.webm" type="video/webm">
            </video>
          </div>
          <div class="talk-body">
            <div class="talk-meta">
              <span class="status-pill shipped">FOSDEM 2025</span>
              <span class="funder-pill">Government Collaboration</span>
            </div>
            <h3><a href="https://archive.fosdem.org/2025/schedule/event/fosdem-2025-6403-note-worthy-collaboration-co-developing-a-note-taking-application/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Note-Worthy Collaboration: Co-developing a Note-Taking Application</a></h3>
            <p class="talk-desc">With Alexander Smolianitski and Yousef El-Dardiry. The story of the 100-day challenge where French and German product teams joined forces to co-develop a note-taking application for their respective public-sector suites, La Suite Numérique and openDesk — design decisions, technical implementation, and lessons learned.</p>
            <div class="talk-links">
              <a href="https://archive.fosdem.org/2025/schedule/event/fosdem-2025-6403-note-worthy-collaboration-co-developing-a-note-taking-application/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Event page</a>
              <span class="sep-dot">·</span>
              <a href="https://video.fosdem.org/2025/aw1126/fosdem-2025-6403-note-worthy-collaboration-co-developing-a-note-taking-application.mp4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Download video</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================= FINAL CTA ================= -->
  <section>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="cta-band reveal">
        <h2>Want to know more?</h2>
        <p>Read the roadmap, browse the source, or come talk to us directly.</p>
        <div class="hero-ctas">
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="roadmap.html">See the roadmap</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg" href="https://matrix.to/#/#docs-official:matrix.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chat on Matrix</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>

  <Footer current="fosdem" />
</Layout>
